{"tid":1355271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不分化不篤灰不割蓆","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:35:37.000Z","uid":68414,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9744cf5e2b21626b7459e4c3fc2d79715d65ee","tid":1355271,"uid":68414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"何妖單野發展得咁快<br />\n有啲中立淺黃話做乜野搞人個墳﹑有啲過份。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我都覺好過份<br />\n但係邊個話係手足做?????</span></span><br />\n何妖家墳比人公開左咁多日，<br />\n佢自己都驚比人搞啦，<br />\n已經派左人去守墳。<br />\n再講，我地手足無啦啦點入到去佢個墳啊?<br />\n仲要拆墳噴漆你估兩三下搞掂啊?<br />\n搞咁耐唔通冇人知??<br />\n唔該大家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化不篤灰不割蓆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0b678b78c1fc81bc58a4c14b650f2da8408045e6","tid":1355271,"uid":157470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中5大訴求<br />\n1.全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4.全面實行雙普選<br />\n5.成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任(包括警黑勾結元朗恐襲)</span></strong>"},{"pid":"47da43c09b41380af21d7a912dffc1aff02ceaac","tid":1355271,"uid":68414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNHksdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNHksdK.png&h=cd76d8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足點入到去？？"},{"pid":"cc4d31bfc8e78078ebedefbaf5f8e4a861ef65ed","tid":1355271,"uid":68414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:33:16.000Z","msg":"過五關斬六將，如果係手足搞就一早比人劈死左啦<br />\n咁撚多圍又咁多村"},{"pid":"969e99a5d54a0008d8e2dcc9054ab8fa545a41e7","tid":1355271,"uid":81934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"[緊急置頂] 724癱瘓地鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"